title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Three, Lighted Tennis Courts Featuring a Versacourt System', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
